---
globs: *.tsx
alwaysApply: false
---
- prefer `Icon` component from kdg-react over raw SVG elements
- avoid unicode arrow/symbol characters (↑, ↓, →, ←, ✓, ✕) - use Icon instead
- use the icon selector pattern: `icon={(x) => x.cilIconName}`
- common icons: cilImage, cilSettings, cilMenu, cilSearch, cilChevronLeft, cilChevronRight, cilTrash, cilPencil, cilPlus, cilArrowTop, cilArrowBottom
- use `size` prop for sizing: "sm", "lg", "xl", "3xl" etc
